<td><p align="center"><font face="Arial" SIZE="4"><b>Our Purpose and Goal</b></font></p>
<p><font face="Arial" SIZE="2"><b>PARENTHOOD</b> is published in order to strengthen our function as parents in the Lord's Recovery to raise up our children in the Lord for His purpose. In each issue we want to highlight the positive aspects of how we can labor to fulfill our God-given stewardship. From time to time we also will identify some of the negative influences which impact on our children and frustrate us from nurturing them in the discipline and admonition of the Lord.</font></p>
<p><font face="Arial" SIZE="2">We hope to foster a common burden among all of the parents of the children and young people in the Lord's Recovery. In the light of the ministry we serving ones and parents must find a way to labor together to train the character and spiritual development of our children.</font></p></td>
</tr>
